    "The permutation feature importance results obtained from the RF, LGBM, and LR models are illustrated in Fig. 4.",
    "Of the 1032 features, the 10 most important features obtained by the model are shown.",
    "In the y-axis of the figures, the word indicates one of the physicochemical descriptors, and the number indicates one of the structural features.",
    "Additionally, the top 3% most feature importance results are displayed in Additional file 1: Fig.",
    "S4.In the RF model, the substructural features of 356, 849, 314, 227, 464, 935, 893, and 798 showed a high importance in the order (Fig. 5a)."
